body:
tyrus snaps include: part two

  • them singing their hearts out at a concert
  • “can you bring me the popcorn?” “cyrus it’s on the table at the end of the couch” “that’s too far” “you’re really going to snap me until I get it for you, huh?” “yep”
  • cyrus cheering in a video he took of tj at one of his games
  • one of them posting a screenshot of a snapchat game they just played and bragging that they won
  • “movie night 🍿@cyrusgoodman”
  • the two goofing off in public
  • tj being roasted by cyrus for his choice of convenience store snacks
  • tj taking photos of cyrus whenever he catches him napping
  • one of them going on their snapchat story to settle an argument about what candy is the best
  • long stories of old snaps on each other’s birthdays
  • pictures of them together on holidays
  • road trip snaps
  • “tj burnt the mac & cheese he was making”
  • recreating their favorite tv or movie scenes
  • videos of them dancing in elevators or public bathrooms
  • random “I can’t believe I got this lucky” snaps

part one
